### Santiniet Blog.
Hello! My name is Santiago Nieto and this is my open blog to talk about some issues that matter to me, feel free to comment and if you want feel free to clone this site!:

```
$ cd Santiniet/Santiniet.github.io
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

### Personal information
I'm a System engineer and computer science student at Universidad Nacional de Colombia.

### Interests
- Programming
- Open source software
- Mixed Martial arts
- Extreme sports
